(156, 0, 2, 0, 5, 'JAMUR TIRAM AYU', 'jamur-tiram-ayu-074206', 'pcs', 13000, 0, 13000, '200', 'jamur_ayu1.png', 'Jamur Tiram Ayu merupakan olahan pangan dari jamur tiram yang diproduksi oleh kelompok tani hutan binaan KPH Tanah Laut yaitu KTH Subur Makmur yang terletak di Desa Telaga Kecamatan Pelaihari Kabupaten Tanah Laut.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"\" work=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" bolder;\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\" style=\"\">Jamur tiram</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" background-image:=\"\" initial;=\"\" background-position:=\"\" background-size:=\"\" background-repeat:=\"\" background-attachment:=\"\" background-origin:=\"\" background-clip:=\"\" initial;\"=\"\" style=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> (</span><i><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Pleurotus ostreatus</span></i><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">) adalah </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\" style=\"\"><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jamur_pangan\" title=\"Jamur pangan\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">jamur pangan</span></a><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> dari kelompok </span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Basidiomycota\" title=\"Basidiomycota\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Basidiomycota</span></a><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> dan termasuk kelas </span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Homobasidiomycetes&action=edit&redlink=1\" title=\"Homobasidiomycetes (halaman belum tersedia)\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Homobasidiomycetes</span></a><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"> dengan ciri-ciri umum tubuh buah berwarna putih hingga krem dan tudungnya berbentuk setengah lingkaran mirip cangkang </span><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tiram\" title=\"Tiram\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">tiram</span></a><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> dengan bagian tengah agak cekung.</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> Jamur tiram masih satu kerabat dengan </span></span><i><a href=\"https://id.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pleurotus_eryngii\" title=\"Pleurotus eryngii\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Pleurotus eryngii</span></a></i><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> dan sering dikenal dengan sebutan </span><i><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">King Oyster Mushroom</span></i><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">.</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" work=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" bolder;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Tak hanya nikmat dikonsumsi, ada beragam manfaat jamur tiram yang baik untuk kesehatan. Jamur berwarna putih ini diketahui mengandung beragam nutrisi yang dapat menjaga daya tahan tubuh dan melindungi tubuh dari berbagai penyakit.</span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://sisdh.kalselprov.go.id/asset/images/jamur_1.PNG\" style=\"width: 440.5px; height: 302.304px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" work=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" bolder;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: \" work=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" bolder;\"=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"><br></span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"font-size: 14px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Ketika berbicara tentang jamur tiram, Anda mungkin langsung membayangkan </span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.alodokter.com/kandungan-nutrisi-dan-manfaat-jamur-untuk-mencegah-penyakit\" target=\"_blank\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">jamur</span></a><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> yang diolah menjadi </span><em><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">jamur crispy</span></em><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> atau tumis jamur. Jamur tiram (</span><em><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Pleurotus ostreatus</span></em><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">) memang kerap digunakan sebagai bahan dasar berbagai jenis masakan, karena rasanya yang lezat dan kaya akan nutrisi.</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Dalam sekitar 100 gram jamur tiram terdapat 18 kalori. Hal ini membuat jamur tiram sebagai bahan makanan yang tergolong rendah kalori. Selain rendah kalori, jamur tiram juga mengandung nutrisi penting yang bermanfaat untuk kesehatan tubuh, seperti:</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Protein</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Karbohidrat</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Serat</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Vitamin A</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.alodokter.com/vitamin-d\" target=\"_blank\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Vitamin D</span></a><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Vitamin B4 atau kolin</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Vitamin B9 atau </span><a href=\"https://www.alodokter.com/vitamin-B9\" target=\"_blank\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">asam folat</span></a><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: -18pt;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span sans-serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">-</span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\" style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">       </span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Berbagai jenis mineral, termasuk zat besi, fosfor, kalsium, kalium, </span><i><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">zinc</span></i><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">, dan selenium</span><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Tak hanya itu, jamur tiram juga mengandung beragam antioksidan yang berperan dalam mencegah penyakit kronis dalam tubuh.</span><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm; font-size: 14px; line-height: normal; text-align: center;\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" \"serif\";=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Sehingga, selain lezat untuk dikonsumsi para konsumen juga mendapatkan banyak manfaat dan khasiat dari </span><span style=\"font-family: \" work=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-weight:=\"\" bolder;\"=\"\"><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\">Jamur Tiram Ayu</span></span><span times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\";\"=\"\"> olahan dari Kelompok Tani Hutan Subur Makmur Binaan dari KPH Tanah Laut ini.</span></span></p>', '5', 'Y', '', 81, 1, 0, NULL, '2021-12-16 07:42:06', ''),
